			Company Description 


			ImageWare Systems, Inc. is a developer of mobile and cloud-based identity management solutions, which engages in the provision of biometric authentication solutions for the enterprise. It also involves in delivering next-generation biometrics as an interactive and scalable cloud-based solution. The ...
		


                ImageWare Systems, Inc. is a developer of mobile and cloud-based identity management solutions, which engages in the provision of biometric authentication solutions for the enterprise. It also involves in delivering next-generation biometrics as an interactive and scalable cloud-based solution. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in San Diego, CA.
            




