GoCloudID enables system integrators and identity service solution providers to rapidly develop and deploy highly configurable, cost effective, modular, multi-modal biometric identity management, and advanced credentialing solutions.
GoMobile Interactive transforms a mobile device into a complete mobile ID using the security of biometrics. This allows development of mobile apps that engage consumers and enable transactions securely with the peace of mind that comes from using biometric authentication.
